'From Cuis 3.3 of 2 June 2011 [latest update: #1024] on 16 November 2011 at 9:27:46 am'!!CuisSourceFileArray methodsFor: 'sourcePointer conversion' stamp: 'jmv 11/16/2011 09:17'!           fileIndexFromSourcePointer: anInteger	"Return the index of the source file which contains the source chunk addressed by anInteger"	"No source pointer => no fileIndex"	anInteger = 0 ifTrue: [ ^0 ].	^(anInteger - 16r1000000 anyMask: 16r2000000)		ifTrue: [2]		ifFalse: [1]! !